In [3]:
df['Sex'] = np.where(df['Sex'] == 'female', 1, 0)
df['Cabin'] = df['Cabin'].replace(np.NaN, 'Unknown')
df['Cabin'] = [ln[0] for ln in df['Cabin'].values]
df['Cabin'] = df['Cabin'].replace('U', 'Unknown')
df['Embarked'] = df['Embarked'].replace(np.NaN, 'Unknown')
